videos.headline: Gerrit Prince breaks a few tackles to put UAB on the board
videos.description: Gerrit Prince maneuvers through the Cougars' defense for a 10-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gerrit Prince hauls it in for 10-yard TD) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: DeWayne McBride stiff-arms his way to a 64-yard TD
videos.description: DeWayne McBride turns on the jets and stiff-arms a defender on his way to a 64-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dewayne Mcbride rushes in for 64-yard TD) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyler Allgeier powers his way into the end zone for a BYU TD
videos.description: Tyler Allgeier muscles his way past the goal line to put the Cougars on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (End Zone! Tyler Allgeier scores 1-yard rushing TD) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Samson Nacua takes the jet sweep in for a TD
videos.description: Samson Nacua takes the jet sweep in six yards for a BYU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Samson Nacua runs for 6-yard TD) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gerrit Prince hauls it in for a 23-yard UAB TD
videos.description: Dylan Hopkins hits a wide-open Gerrit Prince in stride for the duos second pitch-and-catch touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dylan Hopkins throws 23-yard TD vs. BYU) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyler Allgeier outruns defense for a 64-yard BYU TD
videos.description: Tyler Allgeier flat-out outruns the Blazers' defense for his second rushing touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Touchdown! Tyler Allgeier scores vs. UAB) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tyler Allgeier records his 3rd TD of the game for BYU

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tyler Allgeier runs for 1-yard touchdown) 2021/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dylan Hopkins zips in a clutch TD to give UAB the lead
videos.description: Dylan Hopkins throws a dime to Trea Shropshire for a 14-yard passing TD to put the Blazers on top late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Touchdown! Trea Shropshire scores vs. BYU) 2021/12/18 ESHEET
